braceAllman.markdownDescription:
Determines if opening curly braces will exist on the same line as their condition or be forced onto a new line. (Allman style indentation)
#### Disabled

```json
[
  { "prop": "value" },
  { "prop": "value" },
  { "prop": "value" }
]
```
#### Enabled

```json
[
  {
    "prop": "value"
  },
  {
    "prop": "value"
  },
  {
    "prop": "value"
  }
]
```

